      public ClassDistiller​(StructureDiffNode classNode, ClassHistory classHistory, ASTHelper<StructureNode> leftASTHelper, ASTHelper<StructureNode> rightASTHelper, RefactoringCandidateProcessor refactoringProcessor, DistillerFactory distillerFactory)
      Creates a new class distiller.
      パラメータ:
      classNode - of which the changes should be extracted
      classHistory - to which the changes should be attached
      leftASTHelper - aids getting info from the left AST
      rightASTHelper - aids getting info from the right AST
      refactoringProcessor - to process potential refactorings
      distillerFactory - to create distillers

    • ClassDistiller

      public ClassDistiller​(StructureDiffNode classNode, ClassHistory classHistory, ASTHelper<StructureNode> leftASTHelper, ASTHelper<StructureNode> rightASTHelper, RefactoringCandidateProcessor refactoringProcessor, DistillerFactory distillerFactory, java.lang.String version)
      Creates a new class distiller.
      パラメータ:
      classNode - of which the changes should be extracted
      classHistory - to which the changes should be attached
      leftASTHelper - aids getting info from the left AST
      rightASTHelper - aids getting info from the right AST
      refactoringProcessor - to process potential refactorings
      distillerFactory - to create distillers
      version - the number or ID of the version associated to the changes being distilled
